961
01:21:27,508 --> 01:21:28,926
¡Maldita puta!

962
01:21:52,950 --> 01:21:55,160
<i>Pagas por ello.</i>

963
01:21:55,494 --> 01:21:58,414
<i>Tú pagas. Pagas por ello.</i>

964
01:21:58,831 --> 01:22:00,124
<i>Charlotte.</i>

965
01:22:02,126 --> 01:22:03,460
<i>¿Charlotte?</i>

966
01:22:05,879 --> 01:22:06,879
<i>¿Charlotte?</i>

967
01:22:08,757 --> 01:22:09,758
El cuchillo.

968
01:22:11,927 --> 01:22:12,927
Charlotte.

969
01:22:13,303 --> 01:22:14,847
Charlotte, ¡el cuchillo!

970
01:22:26,733 --> 01:22:27,733
¡Mi brazo!

971
01:22:39,037 --> 01:22:41,331
Esto es por lo que me hiciste.

972
01:22:44,001 --> 01:22:46,670
Y por lo que le hiciste a Charlotte.

973
01:22:49,590 --> 01:22:50,590
Y esto...

974
01:22:51,633 --> 01:22:56,638
